---
title: Link with icon
description: Component guideline page for Link with icon.
---

<PageDescription>

The link with icon component is primarily used as a navigational element with an icon as an indicator to the destination or type of content being referenced. Link with icon should not be used within a paragraph.

</PageDescription>

